#   "After briefing the crew on the bridge, Eva immediately retired to her quarters."
    "Tras informar a la tripulación en el puente, Eva se retiró inmediatamente a sus aposentos."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:63
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_fdbd7fcc:

#   "My sister looked a little dazed from the whole ordeal and I worried about her."
    "Mi hermana parecía un poco aturdida por toda la experiencia y me preocupé por ella."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:65
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_ca4a173b:

#   "She looked a little dazed from the whole ordeal and I worried about her."
    "Parecía un poco aturdida por toda la experiencia y me preocupé por ella."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:67
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_cefb8ec3:

#   "I found her lounging on her bed, staring at the ceiling."
    "La encontré tumbada en la cama, mirando al techo."

