#   e "You killing that guard, then later on Glixken..."
    e "Tú matando a ese guardia, luego más tarde a Glixken..."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:77
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_f827933f:

#   e "You killing that guard, Glixken getting electrocuted..."
    e "Tú matando a ese guardia, Glixken siendo electrocutado..."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:79
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_bf5cca09:

#   e "You killing Glixken, killing all those mercs..."
    e "Tú matando a Glixken, matando a todos esos mercenarios..."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:81
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_9310d794:

#   e "Glixken getting electrocuted, killing those mercs..."
    e "Glixken electrocutado, matando a esos mercenarios..."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:83
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_b472cffb:

#   e "I’m not sure I can ever get used to so much death."
    e "No sé si podré acostumbrarme a tanta muerte."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:84
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_089cde96:

#   c "I don’t think you should, that wouldn’t be healthy."
    c "No creo que debas, eso no sería saludable."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:85
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_1daeb04d:

#   c "That said, I don’t particularly enjoy doling out those death sentences."
    c "Dicho esto, no disfruto especialmente dictando esas sentencias de muerte."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:86
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_2c784d72:

#   c "Then again, they would have done the same to us."
    c "Por otra parte, ellos habrían hecho lo mismo con nosotros."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:87
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_da85752a:

#   c "I know it’s a cliché, but it’s them or us."
    c "Sé que es un tópico, pero son ellos o nosotros."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:88
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_f96e1229:

#   e "Yeah, I’m not questioning the necessity of it."
    e "Sí, no cuestiono su necesidad."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:89
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_713053cd:

#   e "If I’m being totally honest, those enemy deaths aren’t the main thing occupying my mind."
    e "Si soy totalmente sincero, esas muertes enemigas no son lo principal que ocupa mi mente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:91
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_a2926f83:

#   e "And I don’t know how to feel about that."
    e "Y no sé cómo sentirme al respecto."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:92
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_552bc011:

#   c "I guess it’s about what happened in the desert."
    c "Supongo que se trata de lo que pasó en el desierto."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:93
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_7cf80df5:

#   c "Between us, I mean."
    c "Entre nosotros, quiero decir."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:94
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_4fef3055:

#   e "Exactly."
    e "Exactamente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:97
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_ce542044:

#   e "We’ve just been through hell, killed several mercenaries, are about to visit a warzone and all I can think of is kissing my brother."
    e "Acabamos de pasar por un infierno, hemos matado a varios mercenarios, estamos a punto de visitar una zona de guerra y sólo puedo pensar en besar a mi hermano."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:99
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_e1ced80f:

#   e "We’ve just been through hell, killed several mercenaries, are about to visit a warzone and all I can think of is kissing you."
    e "Acabamos de pasar por un infierno, hemos matado a varios mercenarios, estamos a punto de visitar una zona de guerra y sólo puedo pensar en besarte."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:101
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_61dc4adc:

#   e "I mean, isn’t that wrong?"
    e "Quiero decir, ¿no está mal?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:102
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_d4a571c1:

#   c "No, I wouldn’t say so."
    c "No, yo no diría eso."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:104
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_67145736:

#   c "I mean, a lot of people would say it’s wrong to want to kiss your brother, but to hell with them, I’d say."
    c "Mucha gente diría que está mal querer besar a tu hermano, pero al diablo con ellos, diría yo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:106
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_1d5da182:

#   c "I mean, a lot of people would say it’s unwise to want to kiss one of your oldest friends, but to hell with them, I’d say."
    c "Mucha gente diría que es imprudente querer besar a uno de tus amigos más antiguos, pero al diablo con ellos, diría yo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:107
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_03bf9c01:

#   c "And yes, we’ve experienced some terrible things and are on our way to even more terribleness, but that doesn’t mean we have to ignore the beautiful moments or the things we desire."
    c "Y sí, hemos vivido cosas terribles y vamos camino de cosas aún más terribles, pero eso no significa que tengamos que ignorar los momentos bellos o las cosas que deseamos."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:108
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_9e227e69:

#   e "Do you?"
    e "¿Y tú?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:110
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_20e89f5b:

#   e "I mean, do you desire me?"
    e "Quiero decir, ¿me deseas?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:111
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_377050e6:

#   c "Oh Eva, you have no idea."
    c "Oh Eva, no tienes ni idea."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:113
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_92522e25:

#   "Eva smiled happily at me and moved closer."
    "Eva me sonrió feliz y se acercó."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:114
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_110cbcd9:

#   e "You also made some promises, back in the desert."
    e "También hiciste algunas promesas, allá en el desierto."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:115
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_f8837b82:

#   c "I haven’t forgotten those."
    c "No los he olvidado."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:116
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_2a567206:

#   c "The question is, are you ready for us to be together?"
    c "La pregunta es, ¿estás preparado para que estemos juntos?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:117
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_1587fc28:

#   "Eva suddenly got serious in response to the question I half-jokingly asked her."
    "Eva se puso seria de repente en respuesta a la pregunta que le hice medio en broma."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:119
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_59d00cd5:

#   e "I think I am."
    e "Creo que sí."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:121
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_f356e7da:

#   e "It’s just...{w} I don’t want to disappoint you."
    e "Es que...{w} No quiero decepcionarte."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:122
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_6fa22637:

#   e "You must know I’ve never been with someone before."
    e "Debes saber que nunca he estado con alguien antes."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:123
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_ebcd7252:

#   e "I haven’t..."
    e "No he..."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:125
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_a788906f:

#   "Eva looked at me shyly, as if she’d disappointed me already by just uttering those words."
    "Eva me miró tímidamente, como si ya me hubiera decepcionado con sólo pronunciar esas palabras."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:126
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_9f83d635:

#   "In that moment, she looked like the sweetest thing I’d ever beheld."
    "En ese momento, parecía la cosa más dulce que jamás había contemplado."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:127
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_169bdc5e:

#   c "Sweetheart, you should know that you’re incapable of disappointing me."
    c "Cariño, deberías saber que eres incapaz de decepcionarme."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:128
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_93dca9b3:

#   c "Don’t worry about all that."
    c "No te preocupes por todo eso."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:129
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_207c60c8:

#   c "Just let me know when things get uncomfortable, or when you want to stop."
    c "Avísame cuando las cosas se pongan incómodas o cuando quieras parar."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:130
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_67b61bbf:

#   c "If you ever think we’re going too far, just say so."
    c "Si alguna vez crees que vamos demasiado lejos, dilo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:131
translate spanish ep018_eva_talk_9e80c38c:

#   c "I won’t judge you and I won’t love you any less."
    c "No te juzgaré y no te querré menos."

