    c "Alguien te ha estado controlando, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:155
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_39ad687b:

#   ve "Yes, they’ve brought me meals, but that’s about the extent of it."
    ve "Sí, me han traído comida, pero eso es todo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:156
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_bf22c8ff:

#   c "There’s been a lot going on lately."
    c "Han pasado muchas cosas últimamente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:157
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_a096b7b7:

#   c "But the crew has decided to let you out."
    c "Pero la tripulación ha decidido dejarte salir."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:158
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_a918942b:

#   c "It’s mostly out of necessity, we’ll park the ship for a while and infiltrate a Sovereignty-occupied position."
    c "Sobre todo por necesidad, aparcaremos la nave un rato y nos infiltraremos en una posición ocupada por el Soberano."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:159
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_fd261446:

#   c "Leaving you alone on a space station with nobody around watching over you didn’t seem like the best idea."
    c "Dejarte solo en una estación espacial sin nadie que te vigile no parecía la mejor idea."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:161
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_dc2937cb:

#   ve "I’m just glad I’ll be able to go out again."
    ve "Me alegro de poder volver a salir."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:162
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_16d8391f:

#   c "Trust is still low."
    c "La confianza sigue siendo baja."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:163
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_048eba8c:

#   ve "I know, but I’ll work hard to regain it."
    ve "Lo sé, pero trabajaré duro para recuperarlo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:164
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_e4a8e350:

#   c "That’s about all you can do, I’m afraid."
    c "Eso es todo lo que puedes hacer, me temo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:166
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_725a053e:

#   "I punched in the code and the cell opened."
    "Introduje el código y la celda se abrió."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:167
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_db2b853b:

#   c "Your old bunk should still be available."
    c "Tu antigua litera debería seguir disponible."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:168
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_887975cd:

#   c "We’re on our way to Taagmar, there’s a gateway there and it’s of interest to the Sovereignty."
    c "Nos dirigimos a Taagmar, allí hay un portal y es de interés para la Soberanía."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:169
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_ca5f9e7d:

#   c "It probably ties into the prophecy, so it’s of interest to us too."
    c "Probablemente esté relacionado con la profecía, así que también nos interesa."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:170
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_99a4790b:

#   c "The plan is to get in close wearing Sovereignty uniforms and see if we can enter the gateway."
    c "El plan es acercarnos vistiendo uniformes de Soberanía y ver si podemos entrar en el portal."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:171
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_40017eb4:

#   c "We’ll be touching down in a few hours, so you might want to get some rest."
    c "Aterrizaremos en unas horas, así que tal vez quieras descansar."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:173
translate spanish ep018_vess_talk_e364a544:

#   ve "I will, thank you [p_name]."
    ve "Lo haré, gracias [p_name]."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:184
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_f6ca08f2:

#   "Ziv was lounging in her quarters, her eyes closed even when I entered."
    "Ziv estaba descansando en sus aposentos, con los ojos cerrados incluso cuando entré."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:185
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_3dae40e5:

#   "I was about to turn around and leave her in peace when she spoke."
    "Estaba a punto de darme la vuelta y dejarla en paz cuando habló."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:187
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_cfe9d5a4:

#   zi "Please stay, [p_name]."
    zi "Por favor, quédate, [p_name]."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:188
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_ce95f944:

#   c "I couldn't tell if you were just resting your eyes or fast asleep."
    c "No podría decir si estabas descansando los ojos o profundamente dormido."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:189
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_89fb8ec0:

#   zi "Neither."
    zi "Tampoco."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:190
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_aa683389:

#   zi "I venture very far into my own mind sometimes."
    zi "A veces me aventuro muy lejos en mi propia mente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:191
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_c30abc91:

#   c "Like meditating?"
    c "¿Como meditar?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:192
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_ab4eb4b1:

#   zi "I believe that is a similar concept, yes."
    zi "Creo que es un concepto similar, sí."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:193
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_b8b60618:

#   zi "I do it to clear my head."
    zi "Lo hago para despejarme."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:194
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_89aefe22:

#   c "I see."
    c "Ya veo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:196
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_e3ccb768:

#   c "I reckon you're working through everything that happened on Uailea?"
    c "¿Supongo que estás trabajando en todo lo que pasó en Uailea?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:198
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_3ee5df04:

#   zi "Yes, the events on my homeworld are still on my mind."
    zi "Sí, los acontecimientos de mi mundo natal siguen en mi mente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:200
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_d5c277b2:

#   zi "I fear for the future, as the level of political intrigue will only increase after all that happened when we were there."
    zi "Temo por el futuro, ya que el nivel de intriga política no hará sino aumentar después de todo lo que ocurrió cuando estuvimos allí."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:201
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_a294b1e8:

#   zi "Also, I think it's unlikely I'll return to Uailea in the near future."
    zi "Además, creo que es poco probable que vuelva a Uailea en un futuro próximo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:202
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_e6adf25d:

#   c "Oh, why is that?"
    c "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:204
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_a952eb28:

#   zi "Because I want to remain with you."
    zi "Porque quiero quedarme contigo."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:205
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_e4ed677e:

#   zi "Your journey will take you far and wide into the universe, and I want to be at your side for every step of the way."
    zi "Tu viaje te llevará lejos en el universo, y quiero estar a tu lado en cada paso del camino."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:207
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_07122baf:

#   zi "The bond we have is special, and I don't want to lose you."
    zi "El vínculo que tenemos es especial, y no quiero perderte."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:208
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_69dea531:

#   "Ziv had me floored for several seconds and I couldn't really think of an apt response."
    "Ziv me dejó perplejo durante unos segundos y no se me ocurrió ninguna respuesta adecuada."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:210
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_96859da9:

#   "Instead, I climbed on top of the enormous bed taking up most of her quarters and brushed my fingers against her face."
    "En lugar de eso, me subí encima de la enorme cama que ocupaba la mayor parte de sus aposentos y le rocé la cara con los dedos."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:212
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_39345667:

#   "Ziv looked up at me and received the kiss I hoped would convey my feelings for her."
    "Ziv levantó la vista hacia mí y recibió el beso que yo esperaba que transmitiera mis sentimientos por ella."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:213
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_3c10fec2:

#   "Ziv's eager reaction to my kiss put all my worries aside."
    "La ansiosa reacción de Ziv a mi beso dejó de lado todas mis preocupaciones."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:215
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_288deb96:

#   "She pulled me next to her and wormed herself under my arm, looking for a spot to make herself comfortable."
    "Me atrajo hacia ella y se metió bajo mi brazo, buscando un sitio donde ponerse cómoda."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:217
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_a513a05c:

#   c "If you want to talk about any of it, I'm here for you as well."
    c "Si quieres hablar de algo de ello, también estoy a tu disposición."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:219
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_8b9aa26e:

#   zi "I know, [p_name], but in this case my thoughts concern you in particular."
    zi "Lo sé, [p_name], pero en este caso mis pensamientos te conciernen a ti en particular."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:220
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_aa99fbb9:

#   c "Ah."
    c "Ah."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:223
