#   zi "I've noticed that several of the women in the crew treat you differently."
    zi "He notado que varias de las mujeres de la tripulación te tratan de forma diferente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:224
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_33b219c6:

#   c "How do they treat me?"
    c "¿Cómo me tratan?"

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:226
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_14d22c56:

#   zi "I've noticed that one of the women in the crew treats you differently."
    zi "He notado que una de las mujeres de la tripulación te trata diferente."

# game/episode018_conversations.rpy:227
translate spanish ep018_ziv_talk_41107204:

